title: NATO's Strategic Concept
itunes:author: Dr Benedetta Berti, Professor Christopher Coker, Andy Salmon
description: Contributor(s): Dr Benedetta Berti, Professor Christopher Coker, Andy Salmon | After NATO published its new Strategic Concept in June 2022, in the midst of Russia’s war on Ukraine, and 12 years on from its last Strategic Concept, this event takes a look at how the strategy was formed and what it is for.
